== Installation ==

Check if you already have the cursors you need before installing any new package. Cursors can be found in the {{Path|/usr/share/cursors}} directory.

{{Package|x11-themes/xcursor-themes}} comes with the whiteglass and the redglass themes:

{{Emerge|xcursor-themes}}



Another package with some Gentoo themed cursors is available as well

{{Package|x11-themes/gentoo-xcursors}} comes with gentoo, gentoo-blue, and gentoo-silver cursor themes

{{Emerge|gentoo-xcursors}}


To install all of the cursor themes available from Portage

{{Emerge|x11-themes/xcursor-themes x11-themes/gentoo-xcursors x11-themes/haematite-xcursors x11-themes/blueglass-xcursors x11-themes/golden-xcursors x11-themes/pearlgrey-xcursors x11-themes/silver-xcursors x11-themes/vanilla-dmz-xcursors x11-themes/vanilla-dmz-aa-xcursors x11-themes/comix-xcursors x11-themes/obsidian-xcursors}}

== Configuration ==

Edit your {{Path|~/.Xresources}} file:

{{FileBox|filename=~/.Xresources|title=Choose a cursor theme|1=
Xcursor.theme: redglass
}}

Cursor size can be optionally chosen as well:

{{FileBox|filename=~/.Xresources|title=Choose the cursor size|1=
Xcursor.size: 16
}}

